## 🌟 Key Features

### 🎙️ Session Management Suite
- **Real-Time Speech Transcription**
  - 98% accurate AI-powered speech-to-text
  - Speaker differentiation (therapist/client)
  - Live captioning & emotion tone analysis
- **Intelligent Session Assistant**
  - Auto-document clinical notes
  - Flag critical conversation points
  - Generate intervention suggestions

### 📚 Post-Session Tools
- **AI-Generated Session Summaries**
  - Extract key discussion points
  - Create client-friendly action plans
  - Generate treatment progress reports
- **Automated Follow-Up System**
  - Email/SMS reminders for homework
  - Medication adherence tracking
  - Progress visualization dashboards

### 🤖 AI Clinical Support
- **24/7 Mental Health Chatbot**
  - CBT/DBT-based dialogue flows
  - Crisis detection & escalation protocols
  - Resource recommendation engine
- **Therapist Co-Pilot**
  - DSM-V/ICD-10 code suggestions
  - Treatment plan recommendations
  - Session analytics & insights

### 🏥 Practice Management
- **Integrated Scheduling**
  - Calendar sync across platforms
  - Waitlist management
  - Automated session reminders
- **Secure Payment Hub**
  - Stripe/PayPal integration
  - Insurance claim processing
  - Receipt generation

