## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- Node.js 18+
- PostgreSQL 14+
- Redis 6.2+

### Installation
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/fakkreddine/mind_connect.git
cd mind_connect

# Backend setup
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Frontend setup
cd frontend
npm install
npm run build

# Configure environment
cp .env.example .env
# Add your API keys (Stripe, AssemblyAI, etc.)

#Docker Deployment 
bash
docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up --build


